headline: Copart, Inc. to Release Third Quarter Fiscal 2025 Results
summary: DALLAS, May 12, 2025--Copart, Inc. (NASDAQ: CPRT) announced today that it will release earnings for the third quarter of fiscal 2025 after 4:00 p.m. Eastern Time (3:00 p.m. Central) on Thursday, May 22, 2025.
